  "instructions": [
    "In a large pot or Dutch oven, heat the almond milk and chicken broth over medium-high heat.",
    "Add garlic powder, ground cumin, salt, and pepper to taste. Stir well until fully incorporated.",
    "Simmer for about 5 minutes until slightly thickened, stirring occasionally to prevent sticking.",
    "Stir in slivered almonds, green onions, and sesame seeds. Cook for an additional minute or two until heated through.",
    "Remove from heat and serve hot as a side dish or main course with rice."
